This Professional Course represents the &quot;real world&quot; of network design and implementation, allowing you to build a network from the ground up by applying proper design strategies in planning (PMP), layer 2 (switching), wireless, firewall, monitoring, and diagraming.


Recommended equipment:
Cisco Small Business Switch (SG300, SG500)
Ubiquiti UAP-LR
Sonicwall TZ105
VMWare Workstation, VirtualBox, or equivalent virtualization software


